description:
This is Operation TicToc, a top secret government research project where two brilliant physicists have been swallowed up in the void of infinite time!  Where a team of dedicated scientists work feverishly to locate them and bring them back to the present! Will they succeed or are the two time travelers doomed to roam forever through the limitless panorama of past and future?
Only time will tell!
name: The Assassins/The Lion or the Volcano?/Mars Count-Down

description: Two American scientist are are lost in the swirling maze of past and future ages during the first experiments on America's greatest and most secret project, The Time Tunnel. Tony Newman and Douglas Phillips now tumble helplessly toward a new and fantastic adventure somewhere along the infinite corridors of time.
name: The Conquerors/The Captives
Enigmas ;  The Binding Hymn of Incorruption!

description: Wall-crawling gets crowded when a new Spider-Man and Scarlet Spider swing into action, and the one true web-slinger joins Spider-Girl to clear up the costumed clonery! Plus: One of Spider-Girl's longtime foes meets his doom, prompting his family into vengeful action! And introducing the MC-2 incarnation of the New Warriors! Collecting SPIDER-GIRL #39-44.
name: Spider-Girl: Duty Calls

description: Volume 2 of the sophomoric yet hilarious foray into the Grimm Fairy Tales universe is back! The first issue left most fans wanting more, it left others wondering if we'd lost our minds and it left a small handful suffering temporary IQ loss. But we're back at it again so please read at your own risk! Five Grimm Fairy Tales stories are re-lettered with alternate story-lines and some alternate artwork to create brand new takes on past Grimm issues that will have you laughing out loud. Grimm Fairy Tales gets the Mystery Science Theater treatment and this time you don't want to miss the fun!
name: Piper Fluberblunton Goes to Town/Drinking Beauty/Golddigger and the Beast/Snookie White and the Jersey Dwarves

description: May Parker has battled the Soldiers of the Serpent before and come out ahead. But this time, they have united behind an enigmatic, powerful leader, and May's spider powers might not be enough to save her this time. Also, May's romantic life takes a sudden left turn. Plus, the return of the Scarlet Spider! Collecting SPIDER-GIRL #52-59
name: Spider-Girl: Season of the Serpent

description: Mayday faces mutants, magic and more! Spider-Girl battles old enemies and new, alongside her era's New Warriors and alone, while a mysterious figure plans his own web of intrigue around her! Featuring J2, Raptor and other Spider-Girl super-peers! Collecting SPIDER-GIRL #67-72.
